explosive e-mail chain.

01:38.633 --> 01:40.766 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
John Yang begins our coverage.

01:40.766 --> 01:45.300 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JOHN YANG: The e-mails
show Donald Trump junior
eager to hear dirt on
Hillary Clinton, said

01:47.366 --> 01:51.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
