Russian government support
for his father's campaign.

01:51.533 --> 01:54.833 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
The chain begins with
message from Rob Goldstone.

01:54.833 --> 01:57.266 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
He's a British-born
music publicist.

01:57.266 --> 02:02.266 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
