the 2013 Miss Universe Pageant
in Moscow, which President

02:03.000 --> 02:05.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Trump then owned.

02:05.033 --> 02:08.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Goldstone said a client's
father, a real estate developer
who teamed with President Trump

02:08.733 --> 02:13.733 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
for that pageant, had
been told of official
documents and information
that would incriminate

02:14.833 --> 02:16.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Hillary and her
dealings with Russia.

02:16.900 --> 02:21.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Goldstone said it was part of
Russia and its government's
support for Mr. Trump.

02:23.366 --> 02:26.866 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Donald Trump Jr. responds: "If
it's what you say, I love it."

02:26.866 --> 02:31.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
In a four-day flurry of e-mails,
Donald Trump Jr. and Goldstone
set up a meeting at Trump

02:33.333 --> 02:36.766 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Tower in New York with Russian
lawyer Natalia Veselnitskaya.

02:36.766 --> 02:41.766 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
