today she has no connection
to Russian government and knew

02:48.600 --> 02:50.900 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
nothing damaging about Clinton.

02:50.900 --> 02:52.733 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NATALIA VESELNITSKAYA,
Attorney (through translator):
It is quite possible
that maybe they were

02:52.733 --> 02:54.566 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
looking for such an information.

02:54.566 --> 02:56.633 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
They wanted it so badly.

02:56.633 --> 03:01.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOHN YANG: Today, Donald Trump
Jr. said he thought he was being
offered political opposition

03:01.633 --> 03:03.700 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
research.

03:03.700 --> 03:06.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
