that seemed to come from
Moscow and the Kremlin.

05:00.733 --> 05:05.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
This morning, we reported on
the actual e-mails themselves,
what the e-mails contained that

05:08.066 --> 05:13.066 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
show the long thread that led
up to the June 9, 2016, meeting
between these various players,

05:15.733 --> 05:20.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
and at the same time, right as
we were about to publish, Donald
Trump Jr. put out the e-mails

05:20.566 --> 05:22.566 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
himself.

05:22.566 --> 05:26.566 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
