again, striking language
in the e-mails, at
one point referring to

05:28.200 --> 05:32.133 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
this is part of Russia
and its government's
support for Mr. Trump.

05:32.133 --> 05:34.100 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
