reached out to Donald
Trump Jr., what happened?

05:38.333 --> 05:43.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MARK MAZZETTI: We reached out
to his attorney in the morning,
notifying him that we were

05:45.333 --> 05:48.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
