07:14.533 --> 07:18.066 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The next day when we were
publishing our second
story, we knew that the
meeting was not about

07:19.266 --> 07:20.966 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
