campaign would look for
damaging information
about their opponent.

07:32.700 --> 07:37.700 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And then, yesterday, we
told them that we were
planning to publish the
e-mail that -- published

07:39.633 --> 07:41.766 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
