that indicated it was
Russian government support.

07:41.766 --> 07:43.300 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
There's been yet another answer.

07:43.300 --> 07:45.466 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So, yes, it certainly has
evolved over several days.

07:45.466 --> 07:50.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
