blame going on internally about

08:27.766 --> 08:30.300 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
it.

08:30.300 --> 08:33.766 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But the question, the
main question, of course,
we are still endeavoring
to find out is what

08:35.133 --> 08:37.266 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
