saying he had no involvement?

08:40.833 --> 08:43.266 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
MARK MAZZETTI: That's right.

08:43.266 --> 08:47.033 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Mark Mazzetti,
Washington investigations
editor for The New York
Times, thank you very

08:47.500 --> 08:48.433 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
